game.name: Best Emergency Ambulance Rescue Drive Sim
game.description:
The job of an ambulance driver is very tricky to manage. If you do not agree with us, give this brand new racing car a try to understand what kind of stress an ambulance driver has to go through when he or she is on the job. Your objective is to rescue people who are injured at different locations in Best Emergency Ambulance Rescue Drive Sim. There are different missions to complete in 6 unique and addictive levels.

Like you will receive a call from the City Hospital to drop the patients there. You will also be called at the highway where a serious accident has recently happened. Be ready to reach out to the City Bank location where blast took place a few minutes before and it is important for you to reach there on time! Oh no! Next accident has been reported at in City Terminal in the next mission. You also have to reach the location as fast as you can to rescue the patients.

You cannot sit for a single minute as you will have to give your ambulance rescue service round the clock. Fasten your seatbelt and get ready to drive an ambulance through the different streets of the city that is full of skyscrapers and huge buildings. Do not take your steps back as you have taken a charge to make your society healthy and happy. Good luck to enjoy an amazing ambulance driving experience and have a blast with your friends without download!
